Package org.daisy.common.priority.timetracking

Utilities for tracking task times and normalisation functions.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    TimeFunctionFactory  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    LinearTimeNormalizer
    Provides functions that perform linear normalisations given using as reference.
    TimeFunctions
    Utility class to conglomerate the different normalising functions.
    TimeStats
    Mantains a snapshot of the TimeTracker and the reference time used to make comparisions.
    TimeTracker<T>
    This class maintains a buffer of the waiting time of last N tasks exectued.
    TimeTrackerFactory
    Factory of TimeTracker objects, it allows to configure the to be created object and delays its association with the executing queue.
